{"word":"G3549 - νομοθετέω - nomothetéō - nom-oth-et-eh'-o - Establish","slug":"G3549","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">νομοθετέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>nomothetéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>nom-oth-et-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Establish"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03BF;&#x03B8;&#x03B5;&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - nomotheteo&#x0304;</b> - <i>nom-oth-et-eh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3550\">G3550</a>; to <i>legislate</i>, that is, (passively) to <i>have</i> (the Mosaic) <i>enactments</i> injoined, <i>be sanctioned</i> (by them): - establish, receive the law."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1772\">G1772</a>, <a href=\"#/G3544\">G3544</a>, <a href=\"#/G3545\">G3545</a>, <a href=\"#/G3547\">G3547</a>, <a href=\"#/G3548\">G3548</a>, <a href=\"#/G3550\">G3550</a>, <a href=\"#/G3551\">G3551</a>, <a href=\"#/G3891\">G3891</a>, <a href=\"#/G3892\">G3892</a>, <a href=\"#/G458\">G458</a>, <a href=\"#/G459\">G459</a>, <a href=\"#/G460\">G460</a>"}]}